 the Palestinian landowners by operating as private security guards, threatening farmers and using violence to forcibly remove Palestinians who come to farm their agricultural lands. RHR </span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt">believes </span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt">that deal</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt">ing</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt"> with this issue w</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt">ill</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt"> increase awareness </span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt">as to the violations taking place on the ground</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt"> and highlight the cooperation taking place between these security personnel and the army. </span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt">  </span></p><p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 36pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:-18pt"><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt">6)</span><span style="font:7.0pt 'Times New Roman'">&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; </span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt">Our legal team works to</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt">:</span></p><ul type="disc" style="margin:0pt; padding-left:0pt"><li style="font-family:Symbol; font-size:10pt; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 27.6pt; padding-left:8.4pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:0pt"><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt">Submit complaints to </span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt">the </span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt">civil administration when security forces fail to implement </span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt">court rulings or appeals committee decisions we’ve attained for the farmers that allow them access to their lands. It is often the presentation of legal documentation